body: "PR#605 shipped commitWorkspaceTransaction writing durable journals to <pmRoot>/transactions/sdk/<transactionId>.json (src/sdk/workspace-transaction.ts journalPath). Two hygiene gaps: (1) the init-owned gitignore block lists runtime/, search/, locks/ only, so repos tracking .agents/pm commit journal receipts - churn plus cross-branch conflicts, exactly the artifact class the pm-g5sx wave governs; live checkpoints/ dir is likewise outside the block. (2) Nothing ever prunes journals: committed and compensated receipts accumulate unbounded (checkpoint-gc.ts covers checkpoints only; workspace-transaction.ts is the sole reader/writer of transactions/). Fix direction: extend PM_GITIGNORE_BLOCK plus repo .gitignore (respect pm-4uqm custom-root work), add retention/GC via the existing gc surface, and record the tracked-repo merge disposition on the g5sx family map."
